Name: TortoiseHareAlgorithm
Title: Tortoise and the hare algorithm
Author: Jean-Christophe Filliâtre
Institution: LRI, Orsay
Description: 
  Correctness proof of Floyd's cycle-finding algorithm, also known as
  the "tortoise and the hare"-algorithm. 
  See http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Floyd's_cycle-finding_algorithm
Keywords: program verification, paths, cycle detection, 
	  graphs, graph theory, finite sets, floyd
Category: Computer Science/Decision Procedures and Certified Algorithms/Correctness proofs of algorithms
Date: February 2007
